    BaseService<T>
    Base Service that performs CRUD operation for other entity
    CustomerService
    Customer Service extending Base Service consists of method for named query
    EmployeeService
    Employee Service extending Base Service consists of method for named query Employee Service performs CRUD operation
    GroupService
    Group Service extending Base Service consists of method for named query
    OrderDetailsService
    OrderDetail Service extending Base Service consists of method for named query
    OrderReviewService
    OrderReview Service extending Base Service consists of method for named query ALong with an method updateOrderBy which is used to update order by employee where set the new value by getting the old data and updating it with new data
    OrderTableService
    OrderTable Service extending Base Service consists of method for named query Along with two methods update and remove
    ProductService
    Product Service extending Base Service consists of method for named query
    StartupBean
    Startup Bean with enterprise bean for GroupService and UserService Along with post construct where we add new group for admin
    UserService
    UserService Service extending Base Service consists of method for named query Along with createnewuser method to create new user When user clicks on Sign up Customer is added to the customers group
